    <refsection>
        <title>Referências</title>
        <para>Milton Abramowitz e Irene A. Stegun, eds. Handbook of Mathematical
            Functions with Formulas, Graphs, and Mathematical Tables. New York: Dover,
            1972.
        </para>
    </refsection>
</refentry>
